WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.250
You built a business.

2
00:00:02.250 --> 00:00:06.125
Somewhere along the way, it started running you.

3
00:00:06.125 --> 00:00:08.850
Every day starts with checking.

4
00:00:08.850 --> 00:00:13.825
Was the task done. Were we able to reply. Did anything break.

5
00:00:13.825 --> 00:00:18.675
You can't step away, because you're the one holding it all together.

6
00:00:18.675 --> 00:00:21.825
We hand that work to software agents.

7
00:00:21.825 --> 00:00:25.950
They run on a schedule, or when an email comes in.

8
00:00:25.950 --> 00:00:29.900
Nobody at a keyboard. Nothing waiting on you.

9
00:00:29.900 --> 00:00:31.900
This could be you.

10
00:00:31.900 --> 00:00:36.725
Every run of yours logged, timestamped, one after the next.

11
00:00:36.725 --> 00:00:39.550
If something breaks, it tells you.

12
00:00:39.550 --> 00:00:42.150
That checking work is gone.

13
00:00:42.150 --> 00:00:44.625
Your week opens back up.

14
00:00:44.625 --> 00:00:47.475
The business is yours again.

15
00:00:47.475 --> 00:00:51.275
Start with the three-hundred-dollar diagnostic.

16
00:00:51.275 --> 00:00:55.650
We'll map what's eating your week, and what to hand off first.

17
00:00:55.650 --> 00:00:59.650
Reach out to Shoogar Soft!
